Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.54,0:53:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were drenched in sweat when our eyes met, {hikaru ase, T shatsu, deatta koi}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.00,0:53:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,shining brighter than anyone else in the world {dare yori mo kagayaku kimi wo mite}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.38,0:53:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand what the feeling was, {hajimete no kimochi wo mitsuketa yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.80,0:53:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was ready for a new journey with you {arata na tabi ga hajimaru}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.18,0:53:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget the breeze \Nas I watched you after the rain fell {ameagari, kimagure, aoi kaze}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.53,0:53:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I'll shine bright enough to keep you warm {tsuyoi hizashi itsuka oikoshite}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.95,0:53:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to write the longest love story with you, {kore kara egaite iku koi no iro}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.37,0:53:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,coloring each page with our emotions, day after day {hajimari no peeji irodoru yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.75,0:53:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like two stars lining up on a horoscope's page, {uranai zasshi futatsu no hoshi ni}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.19,0:54:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop wishing \Nour futures would intertwine {futari no mirai wo kasanete miru no}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.58,0:54:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart, covered in old scars, {kasabuta darake}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.27,0:54:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is finally starting to heal {torenai kokoro}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.00,0:54:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your love for it \Nwill make it beat like never before {anata no yasashi sa de fusagaru}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.52,0:54:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere along the way, {itsu no ma ni ka sukima aita}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.36,0:54:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the emptiness in my heart started to disappear, {kokoro ga mitasarete iku}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.24,0:54:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly being filled \Nwith fleeting moments I had with you {futo shita shunkan no sarigenai shigusa}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.11,0:54:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to look into your beautiful eyes forever {itsu no hi ni ka yume wo kataru anata no kao wo zutto}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.25,0:54:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and smile as you share \Nyour most intimate dreams {mitsumete itai hohoende itai}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.35,0:54:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about how much \NI want to be your knight in shining armor, {taisetsu na nanika wo mamoru toki}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.81,0:55:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it gives me all the courage \Nto take a step forward {fumidaseru ippo ga yuuki nara}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.23,0:55:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I met you, \NI was always afraid of getting hurt, {kizutsuku koto kara nigedashite}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.60,0:55:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,always choosing to take the long way around {itsu mo tada toomawari bakari}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.83,0:55:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My tough exterior has nowhere to go anymore, {yukiba nakushita tsuyogari no kuse ga}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.34,0:55:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by the emotions I feel \Nwhen I'm around you {kokoro no naka de tomadotteiru yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.67,0:55:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, when I learend of your true feelings, {hajimete shitta anata no omoi ni}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.13,0:55:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,my overflowing tears \Nsaid more than any words could {kotoba yori namida afurete kuru}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.06,0:55:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if our paths won't always \Nhave the same road ahead {sukoshi haba no chigau ashi de ippo zutsu arukou ne}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.03,0:55:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm determined to walk with you side by side {futari de ayumu michi dekoboko no michi}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.96,0:55:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a blank canvas \Nand paint it in our dreams, {futatsu ori no shiroi chizu ni shirusu chiisana ketsui wo}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.49,0:55:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching for an excuse \Nto show you how I feel {shoujiki ni ima tsutae you}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.55,0:56:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the melody \Nof our love to stop playing {mimi moto de kikoeru futari no merodii}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.93,0:56:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As I hold back my tears,\N fearing what your answer will be, {afuredasu namida koraete}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.31,0:56:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you this question, made of simple words, {arikitari no kotoba anata ni iu yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.10,0:56:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This bond will last forever, won't it? {kore kara mo zutto issho da yo ne?}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.03,0:56:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings for you are like raindrops \Nin the midnight clouds, {osaekirenai kono kimochi ga nijuu goji no sora kara}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.95,0:56:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with nothing to stop them \Nfrom pouring down on you {hikaru shizuku to shite furi sosoida}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.83,0:56:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my thoughts could catch up, {ki ga tsuitara kokoro no naka}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.50,0:56:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the wind after the rain had already come {yasashii kaze ga fuite}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.40,0:56:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and opened the doors of tomorrow \Nand our future {asu e no tobira sotto hiraku}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.47,0:56:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to make a promise that outlives time, {kotoba ga ima toki wo koete eien wo tsukinukeru}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.50,0:56:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing every season yet to come \Nand piercing eternity {ikutsumo no kisetsu wo toori sugite}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.34,0:57:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When we finally reach our destination \Nafter this long journey {tadoritsuita futari no basho naga sugita tabi no ato}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.00,0:57:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll look back and smile at the love \Nwe nurtured along the way {chikatta ai wo sodate you}
